data.title: Ronald Charles “Ron” Marlenee (1935
data.meta_description: People will tell the story about a man who lived. He was a son, a dad, a grandpa to many. He was a congressman, the best one if I do say so. He was loved by many. -Olivia Helland, Granddaughter Former Congressman Ron Marlenee passed peacefully Sunday, April 26, 2020 in Bozeman, Montana. He was surrounded by his wife,...
